<B>

December 18, 1997
</B></P></CENTER>

<BLOCKQUOTE>
<P><FONT SIZE=+1>We are Warner-Lambert, the company that makes the world
feel better. We try to live up to our reputation in all we do. It starts
with our pharmaceutical products that your doctor prescribes to improve
your health. Then there are our consumer health products that millions
rely on every day to feel good and look their best. And our confectionery
products give people pleasure in countless small ways. </FONT></P>

<P><FONT SIZE=+1>Now we're also helping the world feel better through our
website. Visit our <A HREF="http://warner-lambert.com/info/healthintro.html">Health
and Fitness</A> area to learn how to start improving your health today.
Or relax with a quick trip to a distant land on our <A HREF="http://warner-lambert.com/info/globaltour.html">Global
Tour</A>. Of course, if you'd like to know more about a company that makes
a difference in so many lives, check out <A HREF="http://warner-lambert.com/info/warnerworld.html">Warner-Lambert's
World</A>. </FONT></P>

